Package org.ardenus.resource

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ResourceListener
    Used to listen for events related to DataResources.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Resource
    Used for loading and managing data related to the Java classpath or system files using the SummerLine module path system.
    ResourcePack
    Used to load ZIP files or directories and treat their contents in them like normal resources.
    Zip
    This class contains commonly used functions related to ZIP files.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Resource.StreamState
    Represents the state of a InputStream.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidExtensionException
    Thrown when an invalid extension for a file is encountered, typically occurs when loading resources.
